Description: link libgnat with libatomic on armel
 TODO: check if #861734 is reproducible nowadays.
 .
 debian/rules.patch applies this when DEB_TARGET_ARCH is armel.
 The condition in src/gcc/ada/gcc-interface/Makefile.in could be
 refined to exclude armhf, but the artificial dependency on libatomic
 in src/Makefile.def would remain.
 .
 Autogen should refresh src/Makefile.in from src/Makefile.{def,tpl}
 at build time, but we do not want to Build-Depend: guile.
